{"tid":1105482,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 隻貓又生蚤","createTime":"2019-04-14T02:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T22:04:16.000Z","uid":202997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d576e5f8df17810b5abf981c8cba1a100def101c","tid":1105482,"uid":202997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"屋企隻貓半年前生過蚤，奮鬥左一排終於清左<br />\n一路都有滴開frontline，但唔知點解呢排又有蚤<br />\n懷疑係上次生蚤嘅時候仲有蚤蛋係屋企<br />\n咁啱上次生蚤係冬天可能啲蛋冇孵<br />\n天氣暖返就孵返曬出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔知點解滴開frontline都中招 <br />\n滴完一個禮拜帶去沖涼算係清左啲但都係仲有<br />\n有幫佢梳蚤但清唔乾淨<br />\n有冇其他解決方法🙏🏻<br />\n仲有點樣清屋企啲蚤？"},{"pid":"b30771dcc58ea10103bcaf675105e3acdba442c3","tid":1105482,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"滅蚤蛋炸一炸間屋"},{"pid":"10cf4c3c7e9a79b66578281e3093db226b394b30","tid":1105482,"uid":239718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b30771dcc58ea10103bcaf675105e3acdba442c3","tid":1105482,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"滅蚤蛋炸一炸間屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"啱呀，之前有蚤，沖左連沖兩日涼，加炸左一次屋，接返隻貓返黎前，全屋大消毒，而家未見到有過"},{"pid":"79cb18461aa5b03813ede62d4a9a6e042b0efc51","tid":1105482,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T22:03:37.000Z","msg":"frontline 定 frontline plus<br />\n<br />\nplus殺埋蚤蛋<br />\n<br />\n同埋滴起碼6個月<br />\n<br />\n可以參考依個channel <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/PnGGUXyjp2U\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPnGGUXyjp2U&h=abc9c88b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0edaad00d0a0257c8cb79e881be1d29722039bae","tid":1105482,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79cb18461aa5b03813ede62d4a9a6e042b0efc51","tid":1105482,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T22:03:37.000Z","msg":"frontline 定 frontline plus<br />\n<br />\nplus殺埋蚤蛋<br 